00:17:32.766 --> 00:17:36.269
Derek. look. You're on TV.

319
00:17:36.300 --> 00:17:38.368
See yourself? Say. ''hi.''

320
00:17:38.399 --> 00:17:39.801
No.

321
00:17:39.833 --> 00:17:41.501
l was havin'
the game of my life.

322
00:17:41.533 --> 00:17:47.038
l was--Think l got 600.OOO.
uh. and l hadn't died yet.

323
00:17:47.066 --> 00:17:50.135
And when l started
hearing some noises

324
00:17:50.166 --> 00:17:52.201
coming down the stairs.
screaming--

325
00:18:27.466 --> 00:18:28.967
And it's all on tape.
and l--

326
00:18:29.000 --> 00:18:31.569
That's the tape l had to send in
to--to Twin Galaxies.

327
00:18:34.000 --> 00:18:35.668
Everything l'm all about

328
00:18:35.699 --> 00:18:37.701
by practicing
transcendental meditation.

329
00:18:37.733 --> 00:18:39.334
and l like to see
that mirrored

330
00:18:39.366 --> 00:18:42.469
in the way l apply myself
to the video game world.

331
00:18:42.500 --> 00:18:44.435
in that
l seek to find champions

332
00:18:44.466 --> 00:18:46.601
and watch them grow
and become even greater

333
00:18:46.633 --> 00:18:50.436
as they begin to unfold more and
more of their full potential.

334
00:18:50.466 --> 00:18:52.100
which is what we do
when we do TM.

335
00:18:52.133 --> 00:18:57.104
lf Walter. through all these
years. all the way since 1982.

336
00:18:57.133 --> 00:19:00.803
hadn't continued
as a labor of love.

337
00:19:00.833 --> 00:19:03.268
then there would be
no central organization

338
00:19:03.300 --> 00:19:04.968
for competitive
video game playing.

339
00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:08.236
Why do we do it?
Because we actually love this.

340
00:19:08.266 --> 00:19:10.267
Because we enjoy this.
We're fascinated by this.

341
00:19:10.300 --> 00:19:11.834
There's just something
in our genes

342
00:19:11.866 --> 00:19:15.069
that my group. Twin Galaxies.
raising the banner high

343
00:19:15.100 --> 00:19:18.102
